European Bank Lends to West Africa Environment, Energy Projects

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-06-16T15:59:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-16/european-bank-lends-to-west-africa-environment-energy-projects.html
The  European Investment Bank  will
lend 60 million euros ($84.6 million) to the West African
Development Bank to fund environmental and renewable energy
projects in the region, the Luxembourg-based bank said in an e-
mailed statement.  The funding will enable the Lome-based bank to lend as much
as 5 million euros to individual public and private investments
in energy, transportation, agri-business and tourism.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 